<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7796> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7796" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Leg., lieut. 90. Identified with Plautius in 87 (MRR 2.51) by Schleussner, Legaten 231, no. 127. See MRR 2.29 and 51, 53, note 10; and Wiseman, NM 252, no. 324.\n" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7559> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7559" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Leg., lieut. 87. See MRR 2.51. Badian suggests that he was more probably A. Plotius (7). Leg., lieut. 90 (2.29) than M. Plautius Silvanus (29). Tr. Pl. 89 or 88. According to Livy (Per. 80), he was defeated by Samnite forces (misreported in MRR 2.51).\n" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/4045> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #4045" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Legate, presumably serving under Metellus Pius. He defeated Samnite forces which had joined Marius and Cinna (Liv. Per. 80)." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/4044> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #4044" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "10 He may be identified with the author of the Lex Plautia Papiria of 89, M. Plautius Silvanus." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/3884> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #3884" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Legate (Liv. Per. 74; Oros. 5.18.17), perhaps under L. Porcius in Etruria. He suppressed revolts in Umbria (Liv.; Oros.)." .
